casebody.data:
Horn, Respondent, v. Prior et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

January 11, 1889.) Appeal from Hinth district court. .

Argued before Larrehore, O. J., and Allen and Bookstaver, JJ.

Charles W. Dayton and William King Hall, for appellants. David B. Ogden, for respondent.

Order reversed, with costs, and restitution of the $750 rent paid ordered.
